title: Latvia Gross Household Saving Rate
description: Household Saving Rate in Latvia decreased to 13.89 percent in 2021 from 14.56 percent in 2020. Personal Savings in Latvia averaged 1.69 percent from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 14.56 percent in 2020 and a record low of -20.14 percent in 1995. This page provides - Latvia Personal Savings - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: EUROSTAT
